549
00:24:05,450 --> 00:24:06,040
OK?

550
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:08,410
The second problem is he
doesn't know how I feel.

551
00:24:08,410 --> 00:24:10,120
So there's an
information asymmetry,

552
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:11,703
which makes negotiations hard.

553
00:24:11,703 --> 00:24:13,120
There's a third
problem too, which

554
00:24:13,120 --> 00:24:17,093
