576
00:25:05,420 --> 00:25:07,045
for them to play the
music, they should

577
00:25:07,045 --> 00:25:08,930
get to play it and
just pay you $83.

578
00:25:08,930 --> 00:25:10,470
But, in fact, that doesn't work.

579
00:25:10,470 --> 00:25:12,470
So, in fact, private
solutions to these problems

580
00:25:12,470 --> 00:25:14,673
