R&D because firms under invest,

615
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:51,350
OK?

616
00:26:51,350 --> 00:26:54,710
Essentially, firms don't
account for the spillovers

617
00:26:54,710 --> 00:26:56,910
that their investments
have on others.

618
00:26:56,910 --> 00:26:58,880
So a great example
