00:27:27,340 --> 00:27:29,450
it was because some
dogs got sick in drug--

635
00:27:29,450 --> 00:27:31,128
in the animal trials.

636
00:27:31,128 --> 00:27:32,670
And so Merck went
to Sankyo and said,

637
00:27:32,670 --> 00:27:34,040
hey, we heard some
dogs are sick.

638
00:27:34,040 --> 00:27:34,707
What's going on?

639
00:27:34,707 --> 00:27:36,380
Sankyo said we're not
