00:35:06,790 --> 00:35:10,710
So a corrective tax
can cause the firm

830
00:35:10,710 --> 00:35:14,090
to internalize the externality.

831
00:35:14,090 --> 00:35:18,128
Corrective tax caused the firm
to internalize the externality,

832
00:35:18,128 --> 00:35:18,960
OK?

